title: Florida regroups, sends LSU to 3rd straight loss
description: DJ Lagway threw for a touchdown and set up another with a long completion in his return from a strained left hamstring, and the Florida Gators upset the LSU Tigers 27-16 Saturday, showing a bounce-back effort after losing to the Texas Longhorns last week.

title: Draymond's trip of Edey upgraded to flagrant 1
description: Draymond Green's foul against Zach Edey that the Grizzlies took exception to following Friday's game has been upgraded to a flagrant 1.

title: Windies chase 219 for first win of T20 series against England
description: West Indies successfully chase 219 against England for their first win of the five-match T20 series.

title: Errors and England's Groundhog Day defeats keep stacking up
description: England's errors are undermining a team of ambition and promise and show little sign of shifting in a desperately disappointing autumn

title: McIlroy locked with Hojgaard and Rozner in Dubai finale
description: Rory McIlroy moved a big step closer to a double Dubai success after taking a share of the lead into the final round of the season-ending DP World Tour Championship.

title: Littler dominates to reach Grand Slam semi-finals and sets up Anderson clash
description: Luke Littler put on a show in Wolverhampton and reached the Grand Slam semi-finals in a 16-2 domination of Jermaine Wattimena.

title: Follow live: Tennessee strikes first in showdown with Georgia
description: The No. 7 Vols have only one loss and hope to hand the No. 12 Bulldogs a third defeat tonight in Athens, Ga. Follow it all here, including No. 1 UO at Wisconsin.
author: Yahoo Sports

title: Florida significantly boosts its bowl hopes with a 27-16 win over No. 22 LSU
description: The Gators are 5-5 and have a game vs. 1-9 Florida State to end the season.
